verbose_text: Some animal studies showed that erythromycin and motilin stimulate GI motility and the cyclic release of insulin and pancreatic polypeptides from the pancreas through the vagal-cholinergic muscarinic pathway [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
evidence: erythromycin and motilin stimulate GI motility and the cyclic release of insulin
